{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4a595bc11d","title":"江青给戚本禹的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6b32959286","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":20,"articleId":"4a595bc11d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5387dec24b","name":"文学艺术","type":"主题"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jqjianghua","name":"江青十年讲话汇编","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"/books/jqjianghua.pdf"},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"}]},"publication_details":{"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"16dcca6e78","type":"title","text":"江青给戚本禹的信","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"4a595bc11d"},{"id":"199a0be13a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）江青同志对殷承宗、刘长瑜关于钢琴伴奏的京剧清唱“红灯记”选段和“咏梅”录音的批示。","index":1,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"4a595bc11d"},{"id":"e5dfecaffd","type":"appellation","text":"本禹同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"4a595bc11d"},{"id":"c77c0fbdd8","type":"paragraph","text":"这段录音是一个良好的开始，另外，“红灯记”铁梅的重要唱段没有搞，告诉殷承宗、刘长瑜，说我建议他搞一下刑场的快三眼，特别是最后的娃娃调。此外建议殷承宗和浩梁合作，把李玉和的主要唱段谱唱一下试试看。江青67．11．20","index":3,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"4a595bc11d"},{"id":"f27b9bcdff","type":"appellation","text":"（二）附件：","index":4,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"4a595bc11d"},{"id":"3f189b8d62","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志对把“红色娘子军”（芭蕾舞）拍成电影的批示：","index":5,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"4a595bc11d"},{"id":"a221ed1696","type":"paragraph","text":"此事还是先不急，先把革命搞好，明年再议。请江青同志批。戚本禹江青同志在此件上，把自己的名字划了两个圈，并写了“同意”二字。","index":6,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"4a595bc11d"}],"page":{"id":"b05d2cdd6a","publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"4a595bc11d","start":497,"end":497}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"02eeb0a9fa","type":"paragraph","text":